CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774552271
OL,3,C'Why should I let evil win?': Natalie
OL,4,CMcNally mum focused on joy
OL,6,FThe family spoke of how they felt
OL,7,FNatalie's presence with them as they
OL,8,Ffought for justice for more than three
OL,9,Fyears, with her father describing the
OL,10,Ftime it took to bring the case to
OL,11,Fcourt as "horrendous".
OL,13,FNoel talked of the "most difficult
OL,14,Ftime of our lives" having to sit
OL,15,Fthrough the trial and have her life
OL,16,Fpicked apart and "spread all over the
OL,17,Fworld".
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
