CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774552271
OL,3,C'Why should I let evil win?': Natalie
OL,4,CMcNally mum focused on joy
OL,6,FHe said he could not get over the lies
OL,7,Fand deception of murderer Stephen
OL,8,FMcCullagh, saying he poses such a
OL,9,Fdanger to society he should spend the
OL,10,Frest of his life behind bars.
OL,12,FStephen McCullagh, 36 and formerly of
OL,13,FWoodland Gardens in Lisburn, was found
OL,14,Fguilty on Monday of the brutal
OL,15,Fkilling. He planned out the attack
OL,16,Fgoing so far crafting a pre-recorded
OL,17,FYouTube 'livestream' to play out as he
OL,18,Fwent to her Lurgan home. He had been
OL,19,Farrested by police who later let him
OL,20,Fgo free which allowed him to attend a
OL,21,Fvigil in Natalie's memory.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774552271
OL,3,C'Why should I let evil win?': Natalie
OL,4,CMcNally mum focused on joy
OL,6,FDevastatingly - and believing he was
OL,7,Fan innocent man at that time - the
OL,8,FMcNally family allowed McCullagh into
OL,9,Ftheir home to grieve alongside them
OL,10,Fand even allowed him time with her
OL,11,Falone for around 20 minutes.
OL,13,F"That guts us," Natalie's father Noel
OL,14,Fsaid, "but it wasn't our fault, it was
OL,15,Fhim.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
