CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774552271
OL,3,C'Why should I let evil win?': Natalie
OL,4,CMcNally mum focused on joy
OL,6,F"The fact he came in, the way he
OL,7,Ftalked to us. It is so devious and
OL,8,Fmanipulating. When you look back. It
OL,9,Flooked like he was using us for his
OL,10,Fcover up. I hate him and I will hate
OL,11,Fhim to the day I die..."
OL,13,FHe described Natalie as his "wee
OL,14,Fprincess", saying: "She was just so
OL,15,Floved."
OL,17,FNatalie McNally was 32 years old and
OL,18,Fpregnant with baby Deane when she was
OL,19,Fbeaten and stabbed at her home in
OL,20,FLurgan on December 18 2022.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
