OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774552271
OL,3,C'Why should I let evil win?': Natalie
OL,4,CMcNally mum focused on joy
OL,6,F"It's still a bit like a dream, it was
OL,7,Fjust so unbelievable," Natalie's
OL,8,Fmother Bernadette said of the moment
OL,9,Fthe guilty verdict came down.
OL,11,F"I adored Natalie... she was my
OL,12,Ffriend... we were good friends. She
OL,13,Fwas much loved and much missed."
OL,15,FNoel added: "What he did, the way he
OL,16,Fplanned Natalie's murder. The way he
OL,17,Ftried to cover it up, even coming into
OL,18,Fthis house to talk to us, he's just so
OL,19,Fdevious.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774552271
OL,3,C'Why should I let evil win?': Natalie
OL,4,CMcNally mum focused on joy
OL,6,F"You know how he could do it. I don't
OL,7,Fthink this country would ever be safe
OL,8,Fif he was let out."
OL,10,FNatalie's mother Bernie said Natalie
OL,11,Fwasn't just her only daughter but "we
OL,12,Fwere good friends, and she was always
OL,13,Fwith us".
OL,15,FThe family spent over three years
OL,16,Ffighting for justice for their
OL,17,Fdaughter.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
