PN,44608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774552271
OL,3,C'Why should I let evil win?': Natalie
OL,4,CMcNally mum focused on joy
OL,6,FNoel said: "I think Natalie was there
OL,7,Fhelping us along the way to get her
OL,8,Fjustice. It's not until you get into
OL,9,Fthat system that you realise how long
OL,10,Fand laborious it is."
OL,12,FThirty women have been killed in
OL,13,FNorthern Ireland since 2020. Natalie's
OL,14,Fparents said their fight for justice
OL,15,Fdoesn't just end here.
OL,17,FBernie said: "That's why we speak out.
OL,18,FIt's so scary for women and girls.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
