OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774552271
OL,3,C'Why should I let evil win?': Natalie
OL,4,CMcNally mum focused on joy
OL,6,F"It's not even just the murders, it's
OL,7,Fall the other women who are
OL,8,Ftraumatised for the rest of their
OL,9,Flives."
OL,11,FBaby Deane would have been Noel and
OL,12,FBernadette first grandchild. Unknown
OL,13,Fto Noel, Bernadette had already bought
OL,14,Fsome gifts for the baby.
OL,16,F"We've not gone there yet," Noel said,
OL,17,F"but he would have been the most loved
OL,18,Fchild".
OL,20,FBernadette said the family could only
OL,21,Fnow start to grieve.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/10
